          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">08</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Google Analytics 4</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Traffic analysis · Truly free</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">Free<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);"></span></div>
              <div class="per">Forever</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>✓ What it does well</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Behavioural data after the click — sessions, conversions, engagement</li>
                <li>Native integration with Search Console</li>
                <li>Custom events and audiences for downstream remarketing</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>✗ Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Steep learning curve compared to UA</li>
                <li>Sampling kicks in on high-traffic sites</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Pairing with Search Console for full-funnel SEO analytics.</div>
            <a href="https://analytics.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">Open tool →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">09</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Ubersuggest</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Beginner SEO suite · Freemium</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">Free<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);"></span></div>
              <div class="per">3 queries/day</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>✓ What it does well</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
