          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Beginners getting their head around SEO data.</div>
            <a href="https://neilpatel.com/ubersuggest/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">Open tool →</a>
          </div>
